<p>Sorry about your diagnosis. Have you seen the evidence suggesting that cannabinoids may actually be able to shrink certain kinds of tumors? If you&#8217;re interested there is a wealth of both scientific research and anecdotal evidence available:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.squidoo.com/hemp-oil-cancer-cure" rel="nofollow">http://www.squidoo.com/hemp-oil-cancer-cure</a></p>
