			<article id="div-comment-1316114" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/24028a9495f032285eae63f5f6e2e9c0?s=74&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/24028a9495f032285eae63f5f6e2e9c0?s=148&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-74 photo' height='74' width='74' />						<b class="fn">Alex3917</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="http://boingboing.net/2012/01/10/why-the-raw-cannabis-juicing.html#comment-1316114">
							<time datetime="2012-01-10T19:10:00+00:00">
								January 10, 2012 at 7:10 pm							</time>
