					<p>Sometimes smoking is the only method of ingestion that will work. I wake up several times a night and have to smoke myself back to sleep, and vaporizing changes the effect so that it just gets me mildly high and doesn&#8217;t put me back to sleep. Waking up 5-10 times a night doesn&#8217;t quite give one the time to assimilate edibles, one needs immediate effect.<br />
OTOH, I read link after link about how &#8220;cannabis oil&#8221; cures skin cancer when topically applied and cures everything under the sun if ingested but nobody is actually selling the stuff, or if they are they&#8217;re being awfully quiet about it.</p>
