					<p>Xeni, have you read anything on fasting prior to chemotherapy?  There seems to be fairly solid evidence that fasting reduces the metabolism in healthy cells, thereby sparing people some of the side effects of chemo treatment.  I&#8217;d point you to specific articles, but googling: fasting chemotherapy       seems to turn up plenty of hits from reputable sites.</p>
